          <div style={{ fontSize: 9, color: "#aaa", letterSpacing: "0.06em", marginBottom: 8 }}>Last updated: March 2026</div>
          <div style={{ width: 24, height: 1, background: "rgba(0,0,0,0.12)", marginBottom: 28 }} />
          {[
            { title: "1. Acceptance of Terms", body: "By accessing or using SOFTBOLT (\"the Platform\"), you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. If you do not agree to these Terms in their entirety, you are not authorized to access or use the Platform." },
            { title: "2. Account Registration", body: "You must provide accurate, current, and complete information during the registration process. You are solely responsible for safeguarding your account credentials and for all activities conducted under your account. You must be at least 13 years of age to create an account." },
            { title: "3. Nature of the Platform", body: "SOFTBOLT is not a streaming service. The Platform does not pay royalties, residuals, mechanical licenses, synchronization fees, or per-play compensation of any kind. Artist profiles are provided strictly for promotional and marketing purposes to support artist brand development and audience discovery." },
            { title: "4. Artist Accounts & Obligations", body: "Artists who register for an Artist Plan agree to a 7-day free trial followed by an annual fee of $2.99/year. By uploading content, you represent and warrant that you are the sole and rightful owner of, or have obtained all necessary rights and permissions for, all content you upload. SOFTBOLT reserves the right to remove content found to be in violation of these Terms without prior notice." },
