            { title: "8. Copyright & Takedown", body: "SOFTBOLT respects intellectual property rights. If you believe content on the Platform infringes upon your copyright, submit a takedown notice to takedown@softbolt.io. SOFTBOLT will respond to valid requests in accordance with applicable law. Repeat infringers will have their accounts terminated." },
